title: Release of the President's Medical Exam | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
March 08, 2016

 



Release of the President's Medical Exam





Click here for the report from the President’s periodic physical examination performed during the month of February 2016.

	The physical examination was performed and supervised by Ronny L. Jackson, MD, FAAEM, Physician to the President and Director of the White House Medical Unit.
